data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath ranch located in a quiet, non HOA subdivision in WinderWelcome home to 1625 Bismarck Ct, Winder GA. This 3 bedroom 2 bath ranch is located in the sought after Rivers Call subdivision and sits on a peaceful .77 acre corner lot. Open the door and you're greeted with a large family room featuring a wood burning fireplace and vaulted ceilings. The beautiful eat in kitchen opens to the family room and has a wonderful view of the landscaped back yard. Entertain friends and family in the formal dining room with tray ceiling. Escape the day in the spacious master bedroom which features tray ceilings and a sitting room with lots of natural light. The master bath has separate tub and shower, tile floors and a double vanity. Entertain friends or just sit back and relax on the private back patio overlooking the serene backyard,large fencerd yard two entrances and big storage . Close to shopping, dining, schools and more. Don't miss out on this one. Professional Photos coming soon.
